name: Where's my Food?
description:
Help the little fellow get his favorite foods (chips and pizza) by simply moving towards below the falling objects. Avoid other falling objects which is not a food like rocks. I know it needs improvement and still not 100% polish but hey I just made it in just almost a week of my free time hehe. Hope you will like it and still enjoy the game.
